Update More Commitments With Fundraising

Include more commitments and update the information on the donor for gift commitments with the Business Process API. Use the Business Process APIs on the Postman platform. The Business Process API is an investment for partners to make faster and easier integrations with Nonprofit Cloud.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Fundraising is enabled.

Who: Users with the FundraisingAccess permission set can access Nonprofit Cloud for Fundraising.

How: Use the Business Process Connect API endpoints to access the Business Process API tool.
title: Update Commitments with Fundraising in Nonprofit Cloud
